      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:9:1:2",
      "text": [
        " حَدَّثَنِي رَجُلٌ مِنْ أَصْحَابِنَا عَنْ أَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) قَالَ تِسْعَةُ أَعْشَارِ الرِّزْقِ مَعَ صَاحِبِ الدَّابَّةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Muhammad Bin Al Husayn, from Muhammad Bin Sinan, from Abdullah Bin Jundab, from a man from his companions, ",
          "Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> has said: ‘Nine-tenths of the livelihood is with the owner of the animal’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from al-Husayn from Muhammad ibn Sinan from ‘Abd Allah ibn Jundab has said that narrated to him certain persons of our people who have said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Nine-tenths of sustenance is with the owner of a stumper.’” "
        ]
      }
    },
